window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Caitlin Sera sat down to play a game, but instead, found herself in a world of magic and monsters. </p> <p>Even worse, her first encounter was with an evil goddess seeking to feed on her soul. Courage - and more than a little luck - led to Caitlin not only surviving, but walking away with a God Core.</p> <p>Now, she has to wander a new world with a few new friends by her side, just trying to survive. She is not playing in God Mode, but thanks to her new abilities, she's seeing how well she can do in Godkiller Mode. If she can master the God Core, Caitlin will be unstoppable - but her enemies will do everything they can to ensure she won't live that long.</p> <p>Note:<i> Godkiller Mode </i>is a LitRPG/Gamelit high-fantasy novel. No harems or sexual content, just action and adventure. There is some adult language and situations, but nothing beyond PG-13.</p>"; 
